Elsewhere on the planet. Camoflage's pod is now half eroded away by 
rust.  Its metal housings are all rusted away and most of the 
interior of the pod is rusted out.  

Cam::
She jumped around and nipping at Windlord's heels.  She pawed at his 
leg, scratching him ever so slightly. "Pleeeeeaasseeee. I wanna play 
nooowwww."  she whined.
